用<code>git status</code>查看，整个工作区都清静了。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-96" src="http://localhost:8001/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/IMG_1445-300x158.jpg" alt="img_1445" width="300" height="158" />', '消除Git diff中^M的差异', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '40-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-22 21:28:36', '2016-10-22 13:28:36', '', 40, 'http://localhost:8001/?p=112', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
